de2f1257f2341b01cdf2832a40ed6979c04b86ee89a70f9649ff46bf4255cae5f969a4f8f864d39fed7352edb0184c6b5954ac0f27a20cefce61dde25ad36190  0001-sys-v4l2-Some-blind-compilation-fixes.patch"
